{"id":19015,"date":"2014-05-07T13:20:01","date_gmt":"2014-05-07T09:20:01","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=19015"},"modified":"2025-03-08T11:32:03","modified_gmt":"2025-03-08T07:32:03","slug":"do-not-turn-away-sincere","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/07\/do-not-turn-away-sincere\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Miskin: Do not turn away the poor believers"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Sa\u2019d reported: We were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, when the idolaters said to the Prophet, \u201cDrive these people away, lest they turn against us.\u201d The Prophet thought within himself whatever Allah willed him to think, then Allah Almighty revealed the verse, \u201c<strong>Do not dismiss those poor believers who invoke their Lord morning and evening, seeking His pleasure. You are not accountable for them whatsoever, nor are they accountable for you. So do not dismiss them, or you will be one of the wrongdoers.<\/strong>\u201d (6:52)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2413<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0633\u0650\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0646\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0631\u064d \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0634\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0643\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u06